amendment.description: Manager's amendment consists of the text of those amendments contained in House Report 109-160 which are printed on pages H5863-H5868 in the Congressional Record for July 14, 2005.
amendment.purpose: An amendment numbered 1 printed in House Report 109-160. Amendment makes technical and coforming changes to project-related provisions, and authorizes or modifies additional projects following initial committee action.

vote.text: On agreeing to the Duncan amendment (A001) Agreed to by voice vote.
